    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"114\" data-end=\"127\">Category:</strong> Clan<br data-start=\"132\" data-end=\"135\" /><strong data-start=\"135\" data-end=\"152\">Prerequisite:</strong> Gouken Clan, Level 8+<br data-start=\"174\" data-end=\"177\" />Your study of the martial way has become legendary, your mastery of your martial arts are known by many, and you have longer to go still.<br data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"317\" />• Increase your Dexterity or Constitution score by 1, to a Maximum of 20.<br data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"393\" />• You may select two Taijutsu or Bukijutsu you know that make at least one attack, those Jutsu are treated as Gouken Hijutsu for you, and gain \"Empower: You may spend a Ki die when you cast this Jutsu, if you do, it deals an additional die of damage.\"<br data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"647\" />• You may take this feat multiple times.</p>",
